725583f-a.title: Queens: 69th Street - 59th Drive
725583f-a.text:
Sixty-ninth Street, north from about 59th Drive, showing
at the left foreground a part of the Olivet Cemetery. The
house therein was the Gerner house. At the right is the Herte
house. Ernest Nurge is the present owner.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
